703606f-a.title: Brooklyn: Clarkson Avenue - Utica Avenue
703606f-a.text:
Clarkson Ave., north side, west from Utica Ave.  The building at left, stands on Potter'a Field at the N.W. corner of Clarkson Ave., and
East 49th Street.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
